 184, \"to\": 192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Military members will be able to stream all the action from Paris using their personal devices and computers through ShopMyExchange.com.\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 320, \"end\": 325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999996610768, \"rank\": 3.389264274401518e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Military members\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 276}, {\"ngram\": \"all the action\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 314}, {\"ngram\": \"their personal devices\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 354}, {\"ngram\": \"computers\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 368}, {\"ngram\": \"ShopMyExchange.com\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics take place July 26 to Aug. 11.\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 446, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 415}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 426}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 442}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than 5,000 hours of the Paris Olympics will be available to U.S. service members and honorably discharged Veterans.\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 568, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"More than 5,000 hours\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 469}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 491}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S. service members\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"honorably discharged Veterans\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout the Games, the comprehensive offering features live competition across all 39 sports and all 329 medal events, top stories and moments, as well as live streams of select practice and warm-up sessions and extensive video content including event recaps, highlights, viral moments, interviews and more.\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 879, 