rtinez, the Exchange's senior enlisted advisor.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1126, \"end\": 1130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Robinson\", \"score\": 0.834133500403629, \"rank\": 0.19852288178982933, \"text\": \"Rich\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Robinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1131, \"end\": 1139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tippy_Martinez\", \"score\": 0.861549428701211, \"rank\": 0.1606985943836107, \"text\": \"Martinez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tippy_Martinez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tippy_Martinez\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Exchange's senior enlisted advisor\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympics are one of the biggest events in the world, and we are excited to play a role in helping our military community cheer on Team USA.\\\"\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.0633542928277214e-12, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest events\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1237}, {\"ngram\": \"a role\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"our military community cheer\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are thrilled to once again partner with The Exchange for the Olympic and Paralympic Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 137