ge's online community Hub atShopMyExchange.com/community\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more information on how to watch NBCUniversal's coverage of the 2024 Paris Olympics, clickhere.\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2761, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2699, \"end\": 2711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999621231843, \"rank\": 3.787698443300843e-08, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more information\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2682}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2749}, {\"ngram\": \"clickhere\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"-- Since 1895, the Army & Air Force Exchange Service (Exchange) has gone where Soldiers, Airmen, Guardians and their families go to improve the quality of their lives by providing valued goods and services at exclusive military pricing.\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 3004, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Army\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2788}, {\"ngram\": \"Air Force Exchange Service\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2817}, {\"ngram\": \"Exchange\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2827}, {\"ngram\": \"Soldiers\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2852}, {\"ngram\": \"Airmen\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2860}, {\"ngram\": \"Guardians\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2871}, {\"ngram\": \"their families\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2890}, {\"ngram\": \"the quality\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 2916}, {\"ngram\": \"their lives\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2931}, {\"ngram\": \"valued goods\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2957}, {\"ngram\": \"services\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 2970}, {\"ngram\": \"exclusive military pricing\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 3000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Exchange is the 54th-largest retailer in the United States.\", \"from\": 3005, \"to\": 306